''Ephesians 4:17-18''

Here it is one command after next what to do and what not to do. There is a constant pattern of what not to do and what to do. Why do we do all of this? Because of the following verses. Because of how we learned Christ.

The things you are not do are not in Christ of who Christ is. Connection to Christ is key here. We are not to walk like this anymore. Everything is different.

Does God care about what we have to say? Absolutely! We see words from Scripture and the devastation of what it can bring.

